{
  "id": "adv_card_kor_10_02",
  "title": "fran",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "うーーーーん、ぐ、ぐぐぐ……はっ！？\nあまりのショックで、い、意識を失ってた……",
      "startTime": 7.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "目を覚ましてくれて良かった。一体どうしたんですか？\n急激に血糖値が上がったせいもあるかもですが……",
      "startTime": 15.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.9137415886
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、それが……kana達と話し合って、正月休みの\n過ごし方ってテーマで、一本動画を作ることになってて",
      "startTime": 24.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "その素材用に、それぞれ動画を撮って来ることに\nなってるんです。で、その締め切りが、今日中で……",
      "startTime": 31.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.4099091848
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "終わりだわ……！　どうせあいつらのことだから\nどんな理由であれ一生ネチネチ言い続けるに決まってる",
      "startTime": 40.9603081737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.4815192223
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "「いい歳して約束も守れない山田さんじゃ～ん」とか\n「守れたら一億も借金抱えてないでしょ」とか……！",
      "startTime": 49.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "一旦落ち着きましょう。あと一日……いえ\n半日はありますから、なんとかなるかもしれませんよ",
      "startTime": 57.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.1075956981
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、確かに……一人なら難しいかもですけど\nここには二人いる訳ですもんね。確かにそうだわ……！",
      "startTime": 67.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "え、それ、俺が手伝うことになってませんか？\nまぁ、こうなるだろうとは思ってましたが……",
      "startTime": 75.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.5799310049
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.5799310049
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "と言っても、何撮りゃいいのって話ですよね\nコスプレ？　いやいや、そんな時間ないし",
      "startTime": 86.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.5360273363
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "私生活の動画はこの前上げたし……好きでよく観るのは\n犬の動画だけど、よそさまのワンコを可愛がるのもね",
      "startTime": 95.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "急がないと、もうすぐ日が暮れそうですけど……\n本当になんでもいいなら、ええと、開封動画とか？",
      "startTime": 104.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.2321954412
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "なんかありがちな感じですけど……親近感は湧きやすい\nのかしら。今の時期だと、福袋動画とかもありですし",
      "startTime": 114.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.2637824379
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "あ、何を開けるかはこれから検討しますけど\nどんなものを買っても必ず経費で落として下さいね！",
      "startTime": 123.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.5858945532
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 132.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "近くのお店で面白そうなの、これしかなかったですね\nカード付きのアイドルポテトチップス……",
      "startTime": 134.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.4329439484
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "もっと経費さえ出れば……。でも自分のを引き当てたら\nかなり撮れ高ありますよ。ほら、カメラ構えて下さい！",
      "startTime": 143.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.2829443299
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "新年あけましておめでとうございます。今日は今話題の\nアイドルポテトチップスを開封していこうと思います！",
      "startTime": 153.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "普段、ポテトチップスはあまり食べないんですけど\n新年の運試しとして、自分のカードを狙ってみたくて",
      "startTime": 161.5598140835,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 166.01385088
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "でも……ふむふむ、同じ事務所の子達も沢山いますし\nふふっ、どれが出ても嬉しいですね。楽しみです！",
      "startTime": 172.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 177.3005178137
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、まずはポテトチップスから味見してみましょう\nはむっ……んっ！？　トリュフ塩がかかっているのね",
      "startTime": 182.0036576353,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 182.0036576353
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "香りに全然嫌味がなくて、油っぽさもなくてヘルシー！\nこれなら何枚でもいけちゃいそうです",
      "startTime": 193.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 196.1681814197
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（事前に調べた程度なのに、いい食レポだな）\n（さすがfranさんだ、これなら素晴らしい動画に――）",
      "startTime": 200.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 204.8109586083
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-kor017.m4a",
      "text": "そしてお待ちかねの、ランダムカードの開封です！\nじゃーん……って、麗亜ぁ？　誰だっけコイツ……",
      "startTime": 210,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5122.374724999986,
          "startTime": 209.9333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "カ、カット、カットカット！\nfranさん、その方とは共演したことありますよ！",
      "startTime": 220.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_switch-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 217.7999154731
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 223.6911853159
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-kor018.m4a",
      "text": "そうでしたっけ？　えーと……ああ、そうだ\n確か、ほいほいブラウンってユニットの！",
      "startTime": 229.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "『恋々Poison』ですよ！　番組のレギュラーを\n賭けて戦ったじゃないですか！",
      "startTime": 235.3666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 237.6359034861
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_02-kor019.m4a",
      "text": "あー、そんなこともあったっけ。反応しづら……\nこういう相手が一番困りますね。とりあえずカットで",
      "startTime": 243.8666687012,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9399.999999999978,
          "startTime": 253.2666687012
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 252.2333353679
    },
    {
